====Usage notes====
* Although {{lang|zh|年}} is the generic term for ''year'', years of age are typically expressed in {{zh-l|歲}}, a separate system based on the [[duodecennial]] orbital period of Jupiter. Ages in {{zh-l|歲}} are traditionally reckoned using the Chinese lunar calendar, beginning with 1 at the moment of birth and increasing not during birthdays but at the [[Chinese New Year]].

